      "text": "Well, some days ago João Paixão sent me a link to a paper from D. Pavlovic and M. H. Escardó2 called “Calculus in Coinductive Form”. In it the authors show that if we look at Taylor series as streams of real numbers, then solving these differential equations become as easy as writing them!"
    },
